descript.abstract: 1992 Country Areas (layer) is a symbolized and labeled display presentation of the World Countries 1992 data set. The geographic and attribute data of World Countries 1992 are symbolized and labeled to create the layer. All features are uniquely symbolized based on the COLOR_MAP attribute and labeled by class based on the CNTRY_NAME attribute.
descript.purpose: 1992 Country Areas (layer) provides a common and useful display of World Countries 1992 for a better understanding of the data set contents. Add this layer to a map to display useful information about the data set and that integrates well with other data set layers.
descript.supplinf: For more information about the data set, see its metadata.
